I have been very lucky the past few weeks. First of all, I found an old check for $125 when I was cleaning my room at my house. Then, later on when I was cleaning my room I found $60 in travelers checks (which is the same as cash). Then, in the mail I got a letter from CVS saying that I had an old paycheck for like $69 that I never picked up, so I am getting that reimbursed. On top of that, I am getting almost $300 back from my taxes. So woo for randomly getting lots of money (I needed it). While I have been lucky, I really don't feel all that great because I have been sick the whole past week. On top of that, I'm on my period, which is never a good combination. Today I have to go to the aquarium, then sometime this weekend I have to go to the zoo. Oh boy. I just hope I can make it through the rest of the semester. Just make it go away......................

I'm in Florida. woo. I don't know what to do. I need help.......*reaches out for help* yeah for those of you who ive talked to about it, I hate school. and its not the school part of it. I have no friends and I feel like I am in high school all over again. I feel like I made a mistake going to a small school, theres not enough diversity and I feel like its not giving me the opportunities I want. I believe that everything happens for a reason, and theres a reason I ended up at Xavier, one- I know what I don't like and I can look back and see what I can improve on. second- I met tommy and hes an amazing boyfriend and I don't want to leave him. I'm really torn on what I should do. Could I take a year off and do Peace Corps or something of the sort? or would that be stupid to do after one year of college? when I chose Xavier I thought i would like it because I could start over and no one would know me and I could become a new person. i am begining to realize that i don't want to change who I am, I like the way I was, I hate who I am now. I don't want to continue being unhappy. i feel like a bigger school would give me more opportunities. people say you should wait it out if you dont like it first semester and see how it goes from there. Well i still dontlike it, i still dont have nay friends. these people just arent my type. is it too late for me to switch? i wish i didnt screw up in choosing a college. I don't know what to do. Anyone else been in this situation? well I know liz las. I need help. I need advice. I need friends :-( 

ps. Florida is amazing. :-)

so v-day was amazing. one of the first times i actually looked forward to this stupid holiday. when i did my filed experience i got valentines from some of the kiddies which was nice. then i didnt get back in time to go to class so i said fuck it and went to thw caf and got some food and then drove like a half hour to go to best buy to get tommy the saw II for v-day. then i came back and then went to tutor the little kiddies, and some another valentin which was nice. The kids were kinda phsyco, had to break up a fight b/w the 3rd graders. some of them are hellians :-P then i got back and gave tommy his movie and he got me godiva chocolate. mmmmm cliches taste so good. truffles by the way. ;-) then we played some hexic (i swear im not addicted to that damn game) then  we went to white caslte. omg it was amazing. we got seated at a table with little flower shaped candles and a white table cloth and we got like a menu and they gave me a rose. then they took our picture under the white castle sign and gave that us as a keepsake. they brought us our food and stuff and then gave us cupcakes for dessert which was exciting. oh it was so yummy and i was so excited. I took pictures, I will upload them once i find my camera cord. oh and when i got in his car to go to white castle there were flowers there waiting for me it was so cute. then when we got back were like oh shit i hope they dont die. so he made a maekshift vase which is actually working pretty well. then we played some more hexic then watched contact but then i statred to fall alseep so i left. so update: im getting addicted to hexic, the marble game and Halo 2 on xbox 360. whoda thunk, me, a loser. :-P yeah so its good stuff. then i think im going home this weekend on saturday night. and while im up there im gonna help my mom at the food  shelter thingy with the homeless people so thats exciting. tommy might come up with me im not sure tho. i get to go to florida soon :-) so my history class got cancelled today which was exciting cuz i didnt want my test back cuz i knew it would put a damper on my day. and i didnt get my chem test back either which also probably would have put a damper on my day. i got my chem lab quiz back which wasnt as bad as i thought it would be i got like a c something on it so thats not too bad. still kinda confused on the whole chem lab report thing but its all good. so yeah. tomorrow night, benihanas (sp) im very excited. yummy in my tummy! :-) so things are going pretty well. im gonna take tommy shopping this weekend and buy him some nice clothes:-P i miss my kitty. well i think thats about it for now, thanks for reading if u did :-P peace ya'll

I open you up and place you in my hands. 
I welcome you back into my life by tickling the skin. 
I realize how much I have missed you 
Over these past few years. 

Your call is so inticing
that I can not say no. 
Your beauty is never ending. 
So let us dance. 

You lure me in 
By making promises I know you can not keep 
I listen any ways 
Because I have nothing to lose. 

Make me feel 
Make me feel goddamnit! 
I want to feel alive
I want to be.....

Dead. 


And more shitty poetry from the one and only.
